##  Popular New Titles 
[## Kurokami Seiso no Reikoku Bishoujo o Tasuketara, Ore to Futarikiri no Toki dake Dereru You ni Natta Ken ComedyRomanceSlice of LifeAt Seiryo High School, where second-year student Minato Ichijo attends, there is a girl known as the “Cold Princess.” Her name is Rei Nanase. With her stunning beauty and exceptional talents, many admire her—yet she rejects all advances with an icy attitude. Minato, however, has little interest in romance due to personal reasons. Even though Rei sits next to him in class and works part-time at the same café, he pays her no special attention. One day, Minato stumbles upon Rei in a back alley, quarreling with a persistent man he recognizes as a customer who had been turned down by her at the café. Acting on impulse, he steps in to help. The very next day after work, Rei unexpectedly appears in the staff room—despite not being scheduled—and suddenly demands a kiss from Minato… Thus begins Minato’s bewildering days, swept up by a slightly offbeat kuudere young lady. Nyarotto, Purapura](/title/9cd31469-d050-4523-b1eb-e019cd7f65d0/kurokami-seiso-no-reikoku-bishoujo-o-tasuketara-ore-to-futarikiri-no-toki-dake-dereru-you-ni-natta)[## Tonari no Gal wa Kuchisabishii-chan SuggestiveRomanceThe Gyaru sitting next to me is always sucking on a candy (or lollipop). She makes a "lero-lero" sound with her long tongue, as if she's trying to provoke me! Any healthy boy going through puberty would look at that with a perverted eye, right?! Don't look... Don't look, me! If she finds out I'm looking at her in a lewd way, my school life is over...!! Ouchi Kaeru (御家かえる)](/title/a53f4d4e-91fb-4242-b328-637fb32d0729/tonari-no-gal-wa-kuchisabishii-chan)[## Koi to Yobu ni wa Sasayaka desu ga RomanceSlice of LifeHigh school girl Sayama Umi is placed in the care of the neighboring Hiroi family while her mother is away on a long business trip. The Hiroi household is home to Shoya, an eight-years-older figure she admires, and Umi's heart races at their long-awaited reunion. But the Shoya she encounters is completely different from the one in her memories... A faintly sparkling cohabitation story about meeting changed memories once more. Hagiwara Daisuke](/title/4242c6d3-4ee4-4b0b-9ca0-23bd57952805/koi-to-yobu-ni-wa-sasayaka-desu-ga)[## Tonari no Yasaka SuggestiveActionComedyRomanceSlice of LifeSince they were kids, Kaoru and his childhood friend Toyoko have had one rule: the loser in judo buys the winner a meal. But now that they’re in high school, Kaoru just can’t keep up—Toyoko only gets stronger every year, and he’s stuck paying the bill. Then, after one crushing loss too many, Toyoko teases him with a single remark… and Kaoru snaps. He stakes everything on a final match: “If I lose this time, I’ll buy you meals for the rest of my life!” A judo match that could decide their future—childhood rivalry, pride, and maybe something more are all on the line!* Shimizu Ginkaku](/title/f29af671-80a9-4794-b9e9-e9ca3ed23e25/tonari-no-yasaka)[## Tensei Kaku Gamer: Ouji demo Kateru Isekai Kouryaku SuggestiveSexual ViolenceActionAdventureIsekaiKairu Mitsushima, a middle-aged fighting game player who had his life changed after meeting the "living legend" of the fighting game world, Daigo Umehara, is reincarnated into another world after a traffic accident... This world turns out to be a brutal place where battles are fought using fighting game knowledge and techniques...!? Oginouehei, Yamaguchi Mikoto](/title/23d8002c-8334-4eb4-b5a7-649574c44500/tensei-kaku-gamer-ouji-demo-kateru-isekai-kouryaku)[## Tonari no Gal wa Kuchisabishii-chan SuggestiveComedyRomanceSlice of LifeThe story of a gyaru with ravenous cravings and the loner who sits next to her. These are the promotional PIXIV originals for the serialized manga of the same name. Ouchi Kaeru (御家かえる)](/title/ee9a195f-c1a1-4aff-8f78-b26012330fac/tonari-no-gal-wa-kuchisabishii-chan)[## "Sono Hen no Kusa demo Kuttoke" to Tsuihou Sareta Munou Skill [Shokubutsugui] Mochi Tenseisha, Elf no Sato de Maboroshi no Shokubutsu o Tabete Musou Suru SuggestiveActionAdventureDramaFantasyIsekai"Just go and eat some of that grass over there," was what Aki, a reincarnated person, was told when he was banished from the Viscount Guinas Household because of his useless skill, [Plant Eater]. However to Aki, being banished was an opportunity for him to break free from the constrained life of a noble and enjoy his second chance at life. "Your stats have been drastically increased.", "Skill [Absorption] has been acquired." Aki's skill which should've 'only' allowed him to eat any vegetation, truly manifested after he ate various mythical plants, including a leaf from the World Tree itself. By using his skills, he became a legendary existence sought after by the whole country. After saving the elf girl Saras, he became the only human to gain the elves' trust. Brushing aside the nobles, royalty, and other people in power who wanted a connection with the elves, he became an existence that could represent the entire continent. As for the Guinas family and Aki's younger brothers who banished him, it became difficult for them to get a connection with the elves, and what's more is that they got themselves into a nasty predicament, but... CHIHIRO, Mochida Yamato, sky farm](/title/03bec986-3b8c-45dd-b659-7a2619a086c8/-sono-hen-no-kusa-demo-kuttoke-to-tsuihou-sareta-munou-skill-shokubutsugui-mochi-tenseisha-elf-no)[## Shin'yuu no Otto wo Ubatta no wa, Watashi deshita DramaRomanceSpin-off of *Shin'yuu no Furin Aite wa, Otto deshita*. Kappore Miho](/title/7dbcad16-6ad6-42b1-8e33-8f3f328cd571/shin-yuu-no-otto-wo-ubatta-no-wa-watashi-deshita)[## Chanto Suki tte Ieru ko Musou ComedyRomanceThe surefire way to win a rom-com is always the same! It’s being able to say "I love you!" Akakage, Nanana Nana (七菜なな)](/title/6f5435ad-a6e4-4f15-b607-7bdfcb9bf9fa/chanto-suki-tte-ieru-ko-musou)[## Chie Aru Koibito SuggestiveComedyRomanceSlice of LifeA story of awkward first love between two honor students.
